00:19:13,470 --> 00:19:14,270
Her surname is Wei.

286
00:19:22,950 --> 00:19:23,920
Wei Qiu?

287
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:26,550
The Wei family?

288
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:31,470
Could this be a mere coincidence?

289
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,030
Heng.

290
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:48,600
Weilian.

291
00:19:48,600 --> 00:19:49,680
What are you doing here?

292
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,120
Heng,

293
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:52,550
I fell out of love.

294
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:55,080
You fell out of love again?

295
00:19:58,750 --> 00:19:59,270
Heng,

296
00:19:59,580 --> 00:20:00,880
Jingxue returned to her hometown.

297
00:20:01,100 --> 00:20:02,890
She didn't even tell me
that she was heading back.

298
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:04,840
Is she abandoning me?

299
00:20:04,930 --> 00:20:06,400
Maybe she was avoiding you on purpose.

300
00:20:06,410 --> 00:20:08,030
Maybe she's having fun
outside right now.

301
00:20:08,470 --> 00:20:09,470
That's too big.

302
00:20:09,740 --> 00:20:10,550
It doesn't suit you.

303
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:14,030
That looks nice.

304
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:16,980
Are you just going
to pick her hairpins

305
00:20:17,080 --> 00:20:18,400
and ignore me in distress?

306
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:21,840
You shouldn't focus all your energy
on relationships alone.

307
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,440
There's one thing you should know.

308
00:20:25,470 --> 00:20:25,990
Mi Lan.

309
00:20:35,900 --> 00:20:37,810
Isn't this the necklace
I wore when I was young?

310
00:20:37,990 --> 00:20:39,230
How did you find it?

311
00:20:39,750 --> 00:20:40,990
You have to listen

312
00:20:41,750 --> 00:20:43,470
to its story closely.

313
00:20:54,600 --> 00:20:56,230
So, this is a magical item, huh?

314
00:20:56,710 --> 00:20:57,710
I was able to save you

315
00:20:57,750 --> 00:20:59,030
and Mi Lan all thanks to it.

316
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:02,390
If my mother's family and the Mu family
are the Three Outer Families,

317
00:21:02,510 --> 00:21:03,360
who's the last family?

318
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:05,120
It's Mr. Mo's family.

319
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:06,400
Mr. Mo?

320
00:21:06,600 --> 00:21:08,740
You mean the charlatan
at the wooden shack in Shenhai?

321
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:10,120
Mr. Mo is a nice person.

322
00:21:10,230 --> 00:21:11,640
He even gave us a crow.

323
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:12,680
Don't badmouth him.

324
00:21:13,990 --> 00:21:16,200
Mr. Mo is a friend, not a foe.

325
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:18,490
If so, why are we
engaging Mu Lihua in a fight, then?

326
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:20,670
If Mr. Mo is that capable,
he should deal with her himself.

327
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:22,470
Mu Lihua is targeting us.

328
00:21:22,840 --> 00:21:24,310
What has this got to do with him?

329
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:25,640
So, does that mean

330
00:21:25,650 --> 00:21:27,900
our conflict with her will only end
when one of us dies?

331
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:30,680
But if she does possess such power,

332
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:32,610
is it even possible to even defeat her?

333
00:21:33,230 --> 00:21:35,890
It seems like Mu Lihua doesn't understand
the full picture either.

334
00:21:36,470 --> 00:21:37,750
She's still relying on

335
00:21:37,790 --> 00:21:39,640
Chi Shanying and his influence
in Haidong.

336
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:41,400
It's better to plan

337
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:43,270
as early as possible.

338
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,020
It's good that she doesn't know.

339
00:21:46,030 --> 00:21:47,350
It's best if she doesn't find out.

340
00:21:47,790 --> 00:21:48,790
You can have this back.

341
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:49,990
All of that doesn't matter.

342
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:50,680
Jingxue.

343
00:21:50,690 --> 00:21:52,450
Now, my head is filled with
thoughts of her.

344
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:53,200
Heng,

345
00:21:53,310 --> 00:21:55,120
you have to find out
where her hometown is.

346
00:21:57,120 --> 00:21:58,840
Heng, you have to help me out.

347
00:21:58,950 --> 00:22:00,510
I can't live without you. I need you.

348
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,760
Were there still people
looking for me?

349
00:22:13,990 --> 00:22:14,790
There's no one

350
00:22:14,790 --> 00:22:16,910
except for Mr. Situ,
who asks me once per day.

351
00:22:16,920 --> 00:22:18,160
Now, everyone outside

352
00:22:18,270 --> 00:22:19,990
thinks that the mistress isn't home.

353
00:22:20,230 --> 00:22:20,710
Tao,

354
00:22:21,080 --> 00:22:23,470
Liang came to seek shelter here

355
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:24,990
because he offended formidable figures.

356
00:22:25,120 --> 00:22:26,840
We must protect him

357
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,990
and prevent his enemies
from finding him here.

358
00:22:29,270 --> 00:22:30,270
Yes, Miss Jin.

359
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:31,310
You may leave.

360
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:51,680
You should stop.

361
00:22:51,920 --> 00:22:53,360
It's too dark. It'll hurt your eyes.

362
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:55,470
I have to do something.

363
00:22:55,710 --> 00:22:56,880
I'm so bored.

364
00:22:59,200 --> 00:22:59,710
Guess

365
00:23:00,080 --> 00:23:01,360
what I'm knitting.

366
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:03,230
I don't know.

367
00:23:04,600 --> 00:23:05,790
Actually, I don't know either.

368
00:23:06,470 --> 00:23:07,840
If I'm lazy,

369
00:23:07,950 --> 00:23:09,440
it'll turn into a scarf.

370
00:23:09,510 --> 00:23:10,510
If I'm hardworking,

371
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:11,750
it'll turn into a sweater.

372
00:23:11,950 --> 00:23:14,600
It depends on you whether it'll turn
into a scarf or a sweater.

373
00:23:16,510 --> 00:23:17,160
Is it for me?

374
00:23:17,950 --> 00:23:18,680
It's for the dog.

375
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:23,080
You should stop.

376
00:23:23,360 --> 00:23:24,160
It's too exhausting.

377
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:27,510
If I wish to wear something like that,
I'll go out and buy one.

378
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:32,310
Do you truly care for me?

379
00:23:32,900 --> 00:23:34,680
Or you just don't want
to owe me any favors?

380
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:36,360
If it's the front,

381
00:23:36,600 --> 00:23:37,360
I'm grateful.

382
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:38,990
If it's the latter,

383
00:23:39,030 --> 00:23:40,880
you shouldn't stay
at my house right now.

384
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,120
You should leave immediately.

385
00:23:43,370 --> 00:23:45,200
Of course I can't just stay here
all the time.

386
00:23:47,990 --> 00:23:49,510
Don't tell me you want to go back?

387
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:52,260
Do you know what other people
are saying about you?

388
00:23:52,560 --> 00:23:53,710
You're Chi Shanying's lackey.

389
00:23:54,030 --> 00:23:55,840
And you disclosed
his confidential files

390
00:23:55,840 --> 00:23:57,260
and published them in the newspaper.

391
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:58,700
Chi Shanying will never let you off.

392
00:23:58,990 --> 00:24:00,990
If you head back now,
you'll be seeking death.

393
00:24:01,030 --> 00:24:02,310
Shen Zhiheng framed me.

394
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:03,270
I didn't do it.

395
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:05,400
Chi Shanying is just angry at me
for the time being.

396
00:24:05,510 --> 00:24:07,080
We have aligned interests.

397
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:08,790
He wouldn't kill me that easily.

398
00:24:09,550 --> 00:24:10,680
Just forget about it.

399
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:13,680
Even if Chi Shanying doesn't kill you,
Shen Zhiheng will.

400
00:24:14,610 --> 00:24:16,550
You should come to my hometown
with me tomorrow.

401
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,440
At least you won't starve.

402
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,310
There's no point in escaping.

403
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:22,840
So what if I'm a lackey?

404
00:24:23,100 --> 00:24:24,470
The result will be the same anyway.

405
00:24:24,530 --> 00:24:26,470
If so, I would rather
take the preemptive strike.

406
00:24:26,470 --> 00:24:27,610
At least I have a foundation.

407
00:24:27,750 --> 00:24:28,950
Chi Shanying admires my talent.

408
00:24:29,020 --> 00:24:30,790
As long as he's willing
to give me a chance,

409
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,640
I'll be able to make a comeback.

410
00:24:33,900 --> 00:24:35,400
Why are you trying to make a comeback?

411
00:24:35,860 --> 00:24:37,390
If you want money, I can give you that.

412
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:38,790
You don't need to make a comeback.

413
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:40,120
I have to!

414
00:24:40,360 --> 00:24:41,950
I must make a comeback!

415
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,640
I don't want money.

416
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,510
I want power.

417
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:48,750
You're unreasonable.

418
00:25:00,080 --> 00:25:02,400
I predict that she's hiding
from you on purpose.

419
00:25:04,030 --> 00:25:05,550
But why?

420
00:25:05,990 --> 00:25:07,030
I'm a good boy.

421
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:08,190
I didn't make her angry.

422
00:25:08,710 --> 00:25:09,400
Heng,

423
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:11,400
did you release Li Yingliang or not?

424
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:12,840
I've already answered

425
00:25:12,840 --> 00:25:14,710
that question 100 times.

426
00:25:15,270 --> 00:25:16,470
He's not here.

427
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:19,990
You should try calling
the Jin family again.

428
00:25:20,550 --> 00:25:21,990
I already called them this morning.

429
00:25:21,990 --> 00:25:23,080
No one picked up.

430
00:25:23,360 --> 00:25:24,550
You should try again.

431
00:25:30,600 --> 00:25:32,200
Hello, this is the Jin Mansion.

432
00:25:32,470 --> 00:25:33,440
Hello, Tao.

433
00:25:33,550 --> 00:25:34,510
It's me, Situ Weilian.

434
00:25:34,990 --> 00:25:36,840
Where exactly did Jingxue go?

435
00:25:37,360 --> 00:25:38,030
I don't know.

436
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:40,360
Don't tell me she's in trouble?

437
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:41,750
I don't know.

438
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:43,840
When will she come back, then?

439
00:25:43,880 --> 00:25:44,840
I'm not sure.

440
00:25:45,510 --> 00:25:46,120
Fine.

441
00:25:46,270 --> 00:25:47,230
Alright. Goodbye.

442
00:25:51,990 --> 00:25:54,200
Miss Jin, Dr. Situ called us just now.

443
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:56,670
He was asking about your condition
and when you would come back.

444
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:57,890
I told him that I knew nothing.

445
00:26:03,950 --> 00:26:05,120
Situ Weilian

446
00:26:05,120 --> 00:26:06,470
is quite devoted to you, huh?

447
00:26:06,610 --> 00:26:08,080
There are plenty of people like him.

448
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:12,200
If so, between you and Shen Zhiheng,

449
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:13,790
who is more important
in his heart?

450
00:26:13,790 --> 00:26:15,230
What kind of question was that?

451
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,880
Maybe it's me.

452
00:26:25,700 --> 00:26:27,920
If so, can you tell him to come here
and do me a favor?

453
00:26:29,510 --> 00:26:30,840
What do you want him to do?

454
00:26:31,080 --> 00:26:33,030
Deliver a letter to Chi Shanying
on my behalf.

455
00:26:39,120 --> 00:26:40,200
Hello.

456
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:42,030
Hello, Miss Tao.

457
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:42,710
It's me again.

458
00:26:43,120 --> 00:26:44,880
Is Jingxue trying
to hide from me at home?

459
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:46,200
Mr. Situ.

460
00:26:46,990 --> 00:26:48,950
Miss Jin isn't home.

461
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:49,920
Fine, then.

462
00:26:50,270 --> 00:26:51,640
When will she come back, then?

463
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,840
Mr. Situ,

464
00:26:52,990 --> 00:26:54,230
I've told you many times.

465
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:55,510
I have no idea

466
00:26:55,510 --> 00:26:56,750
when Miss Jin will come back.

467
00:26:57,790 --> 00:26:58,440
Alright, then.

468
00:26:58,680 --> 00:26:59,470
You must tell me

469
00:26:59,470 --> 00:27:00,920
immediately when she's back, then.

470
00:27:01,120 --> 00:27:02,750
Alright, Mr. Situ.

471
00:27:03,270 --> 00:27:03,920
Goodbye.

472
00:27:07,080 --> 00:27:09,310
Hello, Situ. This is Jingxue speaking.

473
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:10,360
Jingxue?

474
00:27:10,470 --> 00:27:11,400
You're back?

475
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:15,190
I went to attend to some businesses.

476
00:27:15,360 --> 00:27:16,470
I just came back.

477
00:27:16,470 --> 00:27:18,360
You should come when you're free.

478
00:27:18,370 --> 00:27:19,890
Alright. I'll head there right now.

479
00:27:26,560 --> 00:27:28,480
Heng, you're amazing!

480
00:27:29,310 --> 00:27:30,200
I'll make a move first.

481
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:33,270
So, that menace

482
00:27:33,510 --> 00:27:34,710
was hiding in the Jin family.

483
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:37,120
Are you worried about Weilian?

484
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:41,030
What's there to worry about him?

485
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:49,680
Why are you frowning, then?

486
00:27:50,230 --> 00:27:51,510
I don't wish to kill.

487
00:27:52,270 --> 00:27:52,950
I can...

488
00:27:52,950 --> 00:27:53,950
No, you can't.

489
00:28:02,820 --> 00:28:04,200
Mr. Situ, you're here.

490
00:28:04,260 --> 00:28:04,990
Where's Jingxue?

491
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,400
Miss Jin is waiting for you inside.

492
00:28:09,920 --> 00:28:10,680
Jingxue.

493
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:12,120
Weilian, you're here.

494
00:28:13,270 --> 00:28:14,550
You made me worried.

495
00:28:16,710 --> 00:28:18,440
I thought I would never see you again.

496
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:19,790
When I heard your voice,

497
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:21,710
I wanted to rush here
as soon as possible.

498
00:28:21,710 --> 00:28:22,600
Dr. Situ.

499
00:28:22,950 --> 00:28:23,880
Long time no see.

500
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:27,360
Why do you still haunt me to no end?

501
00:28:34,440 --> 00:28:35,360
What happened to you?

502
00:28:36,030 --> 00:28:37,360
Did Shen Zhiheng set you free?

503
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:39,230
No.

504
00:28:40,710 --> 00:28:42,160
I escaped by myself.

505
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:44,600
Jingxue,

506
00:28:44,750 --> 00:28:46,200
I did tell Shen Zhiheng

507
00:28:46,230 --> 00:28:47,310
to release Li Yingliang.

508
00:28:47,640 --> 00:28:48,920
He said yes on the surface,

509
00:28:48,950 --> 00:28:49,950
but he didn't do it.

510
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:50,990
I know.

511
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:52,840
Shen Zhiheng was untrustworthy.

512
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:54,120
It's his fault.

513
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:55,640
I'm already grateful to you

514
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,840
that you made a plea to him

515
00:28:56,950 --> 00:28:57,880
for Liang's sake.

516
00:28:59,710 --> 00:29:01,790
Dr. Situ, I have something urgent

517
00:29:01,790 --> 00:29:03,190
to discuss with you
in private.

518
00:29:03,410 --> 00:29:06,190
You already escaped from the place.
Why are you still looking for me?

519
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:08,600
Don't tell me
you want me to be your mediator again?

520
00:29:09,230 --> 00:29:10,640
No. Don't even think about it.

521
00:29:10,700 --> 00:29:12,630
I haven't even reconciled
with Shen Zhiheng yet.

522
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:14,080
He never smiled at me.

523
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,790
No. Dr. Situ, you misunderstood me.

524
00:29:15,900 --> 00:29:17,980
I have something more important
to discuss with you.

525
00:29:17,990 --> 00:29:19,360
Please give me a chance.

526
00:29:22,120 --> 00:29:22,710
Situ,

527
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:24,680
why don't you hear him out first?

528
00:29:25,030 --> 00:29:26,310
If he dares to spout nonsense,

529
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,550
you can just ignore him.

530
00:29:30,270 --> 00:29:31,160
Dr. Situ.

531
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,640
(First rule, no bloodsucking allowed
without apparent reason)

532
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:42,550
Try and read them.

533
00:29:43,900 --> 00:29:44,990
I don't recognize the words.

534
00:29:45,710 --> 00:29:47,230
Try and recognize
as many as you can.

535
00:29:47,540 --> 00:29:48,840
It's vital to learn how to read.

536
00:29:52,120 --> 00:29:54,990
No. No. No.

537
00:29:54,990 --> 00:29:56,750
People. People...

538
00:29:57,470 --> 00:29:58,230
One, two,

539
00:29:58,230 --> 00:29:59,160
three, four, five, six.

540
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:05,160
Do not hurt others
without apparent reason.

541
00:30:05,790 --> 00:30:07,230
Do not show your true form

542
00:30:07,230 --> 00:30:09,030
in front of strangers.

543
00:30:09,710 --> 00:30:11,680
Why must we hide ourselves?

544
00:30:12,310 --> 00:30:14,120
We're much stronger than them.

545
00:30:16,750 --> 00:30:17,680
In this world,

546
00:30:17,880 --> 00:30:19,030
we're the minority.

547
00:30:19,550 --> 00:30:20,880
If we reveal ourselves,

548
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:22,880
we'll be ostracized and eliminated.

549
00:30:23,300 --> 00:30:25,300
The same rule hasn't changed
since ancient times.

550
00:30:25,320 --> 00:30:27,990
We don't need to provoke
the masses and their rules.

551
00:30:29,790 --> 00:30:31,400
But even if I don't kill anyone,

552
00:30:31,750 --> 00:30:33,200
they'll still die in the future.

553
00:30:34,230 --> 00:30:35,600
Mi Lan, it's different.

554
00:30:35,950 --> 00:30:37,160
Once you kill the first target,

555
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:39,160
you'll start to kill them
one after another.

556
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:42,150
Once, you thought you could
know black from white.

557
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:42,990
In the end,

558
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:45,360
you won't be able
to differentiate between them.

559
00:30:48,550 --> 00:30:49,950
If a person can't even choose

560
00:30:49,950 --> 00:30:51,400
to be kind,

561
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:53,400
he'll cease to be a human.

562
00:30:54,550 --> 00:30:56,440
Humans are different from animals.

563
00:30:58,750 --> 00:30:59,710
Fine.

564
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:01,440
I promise.

565
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:05,790
Take it back and stick it
in your room.

566
00:31:06,120 --> 00:31:07,550
Read it at least thrice per day.

567
00:31:08,710 --> 00:31:09,710
That's difficult.

568
00:31:09,750 --> 00:31:11,120
But you gave me your promise.

569
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:38,790
Dr. Situ, have a seat.

570
00:31:42,270 --> 00:31:43,710
If you have anything to say,

571
00:31:44,030 --> 00:31:45,230
you should cut to the chase.

572
00:31:45,550 --> 00:31:46,440
Dr. Situ,

573
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:48,440
I remember I promised to give you

574
00:31:49,030 --> 00:31:50,310
50,000 yuan last time.

575
00:31:51,510 --> 00:31:53,600
After that, I was
kidnapped by Shen Zhiheng.

576
00:31:55,360 --> 00:31:57,120
But even now, you haven't

577
00:31:57,230 --> 00:31:58,440
given me the money yet.

578
00:31:59,120 --> 00:31:59,790
It's because

579
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:01,400
I cannot show myself in public.

580
00:32:01,550 --> 00:32:03,120
I can't manage my assets.

581
00:32:03,320 --> 00:32:05,990
So I was thinking that I wanted you
to do me another similar favor.

582
00:32:06,750 --> 00:32:08,030
Once I can show myself in public,

583
00:32:08,030 --> 00:32:09,400
I'll give you the 50,000 yuan.

584
00:32:11,470 --> 00:32:12,360
So, you want me

585
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,920
to do you a favor for free, huh?

586
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:21,550
Jin Jingxue.

587
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:25,440
What has this got to do with Jingxue?

588
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:27,950
It has nothing to do with her.

589
00:32:28,990 --> 00:32:30,680
But if you're willing to help me out,

590
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:34,510
I'm willing to be the matchmaker
between you two.

591
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:35,580
Do you make the call here?

592
00:32:35,990 --> 00:32:37,200
I do.

593
00:32:39,230 --> 00:32:40,790
Are you going to give her to me?

594
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:44,470
That's not how we put it.

595
00:32:45,750 --> 00:32:46,790
She's a living person.

596
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:48,510
She's not an object.

597
00:32:49,440 --> 00:32:51,310
I'm just saying that I can help you out.

598
00:33:05,300 --> 00:33:08,030
Regarding the kind of person she is
and the kind of person she likes,

599
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:10,310
I know them better than her.

600
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:12,310
I can help you out.

601
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:14,360
I can make her fall for you.

602
00:33:21,600 --> 00:33:23,440
Do you even know
what you're saying right now?

603
00:33:24,030 --> 00:33:25,440
Isn't your wish to spend your life

604
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,710
with Miss Jin?

605
00:33:28,750 --> 00:33:30,120
You're such a scum.

606
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:32,490
Do you believe that
I'll tell Jingxue about this?

607
00:33:33,510 --> 00:33:34,550
And then?

608
00:33:35,230 --> 00:33:37,510
She'd know that she fell in love
with the wrong person

609
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:38,790
and was wrong about him!

610
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,230
And then?

611
00:33:49,120 --> 00:33:49,880
Buddy,

612
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:52,950
when I was 12,

613
00:33:52,990 --> 00:33:54,550
Mr. Jin became my godfather.

614
00:33:54,550 --> 00:33:55,590
I joined the Jin family.

615
00:33:56,750 --> 00:33:57,750
Miss Jin knew clearly

616
00:33:57,920 --> 00:33:59,400
the kind of person I was.

617
00:33:59,950 --> 00:34:01,080
Do you think she doesn't know

618
00:34:01,080 --> 00:34:02,030
that I'm a bad egg?

619
00:34:02,710 --> 00:34:04,200
It's only because she loves me.

620
00:34:04,600 --> 00:34:06,710
That's why she thinks
I have bitter reasons

621
00:34:06,710 --> 00:34:07,510
for everything I do.

622
00:34:08,390 --> 00:34:08,870
In her eyes,

623
00:34:08,870 --> 00:34:10,600
I can always be forgiven.

624
00:34:11,270 --> 00:34:12,350
She's so nice to you.

625
00:34:12,910 --> 00:34:14,040
Why didn't you love her back?

626
00:34:20,350 --> 00:34:22,040
I don't deserve to talk about love.

627
00:34:22,350 --> 00:34:23,870
I'm not a good match for her.

628
00:34:24,830 --> 00:34:27,120
She can be married
to all the rich sons in the world.

629
00:34:27,640 --> 00:34:29,120
But she cannot be married to me.

630
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:34,270
Is there something wrong with you?

631
00:34:34,350 --> 00:34:35,790
But you've done well.

632
00:34:36,750 --> 00:34:37,480
All these years,

633
00:34:37,560 --> 00:34:39,790
countless men have flocked
toward Miss Jin.

634
00:34:39,870 --> 00:34:41,640
I never liked any of them.

635
00:34:42,040 --> 00:34:43,230
But you're different.

636
00:34:44,350 --> 00:34:45,560
You're sincere.

637
00:34:45,710 --> 00:34:47,560
So, what exactly do you want me to do?

638
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:49,430
I won't commit any evil deeds.

639
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:51,080
Thanks to Shen Zhiheng,

640
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,640
everyone is out to get me.

641
00:34:53,310 --> 00:34:55,780
Chi Shanying captured Li Guisheng
to force me to show myself.

642
00:34:55,900 --> 00:34:57,790
The person who caused the trouble
has to end it.

643
00:34:58,200 --> 00:34:59,870
If I wish to resolve this issue,

644
00:34:59,870 --> 00:35:02,000
I have to start with Shen Zhiheng.

645
00:35:02,700 --> 00:35:04,990
I can't afford to offend
Shen Zhiheng for your sake again.

646
00:35:05,390 --> 00:35:06,040
Farewell.

647
00:35:06,230 --> 00:35:08,390
There's no need for me
to resort to such dirty tricks.

648
00:35:08,830 --> 00:35:10,790
Don't worry. This time,
you won't offend him.

649
00:35:11,350 --> 00:35:13,270
You can claim credit
in front of him instead.

650
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:16,310
Can you finish your words in one go?

651
00:35:16,600 --> 00:35:17,640
Stop wasting my time here.

652
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:20,080
I'm here for Jingxue's sake,
not your sake.

653
00:35:20,790 --> 00:35:22,480
I want you to be my messenger.

654
00:35:22,910 --> 00:35:24,750
Contact Chi Shanying on my behalf.

655
00:35:25,120 --> 00:35:27,310
Once Chi Shanying agrees to help us out,

656
00:35:27,390 --> 00:35:28,790
we'll set a trap

657
00:35:29,160 --> 00:35:30,350
and capture Shen Zhiheng.

658
00:35:30,350 --> 00:35:31,640
Once Shen Zhiheng is captured,

659
00:35:31,710 --> 00:35:33,040
I can show myself in public again.

660
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:36,520
You want me to capture
Shen Zhiheng for you?

661
00:35:36,610 --> 00:35:38,080
Are you crazy?
Or am I the crazy one?

662
00:35:38,160 --> 00:35:39,960
Don't worry.
This time, I won't harm him.

663
00:35:39,970 --> 00:35:41,750
I'll only request him
to own up to his crime

664
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:44,350
and clear my name
in front of Chi Shanying.

665
00:35:44,520 --> 00:35:46,350
By then, I have ways
to help you leave.

666
00:35:46,390 --> 00:35:47,790
You guys can go wherever you like.

667
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:49,750
You can leave Haidong
and go somewhere far away.

668
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:52,890
If you can't bear to part with Miss Jin,
I can recommend you to Chi Shanying.

669
00:35:53,430 --> 00:35:55,390
You'll have a bright future
if you serve him.

670
00:35:56,160 --> 00:35:58,080
You can only dupe kids
with that stupid plan.

671
00:35:58,200 --> 00:35:59,990
You want me to help you
capture Shen Zhiheng?

672
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:02,520
I'm afraid you'll silence me
after capturing him.

673
00:36:02,870 --> 00:36:04,560
There's no need to silence you.

674
00:36:04,790 --> 00:36:06,000
If I do,

675
00:36:06,040 --> 00:36:07,750
Shen Zhiheng will silence me.

676
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:10,330
I believe that you won't tell him
about our plan, right?

677
00:36:11,350 --> 00:36:13,120
But Shen Zhiheng hates you to the core.

678
00:36:13,430 --> 00:36:15,000
Why would he follow your will?

679
00:36:15,300 --> 00:36:17,050
He'll own up to his crime
just as you want?

680
00:36:17,310 --> 00:36:18,910
That's just a superficial process.

681
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,270
In reality,

682
00:36:21,390 --> 00:36:23,790
Mu Lihua, Chi Shanying, and him

683
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:25,600
will each take a step back after that.

684
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:28,000
They'll give each other an out.

685
00:36:28,960 --> 00:36:30,640
Don't you agree?

686
00:36:38,810 --> 00:36:40,190
May we have a pleasant cooperation.

687
00:36:43,120 --> 00:36:44,310
This is not a cooperation.

688
00:36:44,700 --> 00:36:46,480
I'll stop the plan immediately
if I find out

689
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,200
