690
00:36:48,830 --> 00:36:50,870
Don't worry. I understand.

691
00:36:51,200 --> 00:36:52,870
I won't put you on the spot.

692
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:12,430
Are you guys done?

693
00:37:12,680 --> 00:37:14,060
Jingxue, I'll make a move first.

694
00:37:21,160 --> 00:37:22,040
Did he agree to it?

695
00:37:23,040 --> 00:37:23,640
Yes.

696
00:37:24,830 --> 00:37:26,480
What did you offer him?

697
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:28,160
I offered him money.

698
00:37:28,600 --> 00:37:30,010
Moreover,
he didn't take any risks.

699
00:37:30,390 --> 00:37:31,430
It's just a small favor.

700
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,960
He's a nice person. He's pure too.

701
00:37:34,830 --> 00:37:35,960
You mustn't harm him.

702
00:37:36,510 --> 00:37:37,830
You're quite concerned about him.

703
00:37:38,560 --> 00:37:39,960
Yeah. What's wrong with that?

704
00:37:43,680 --> 00:37:45,080
I'm not immoral, you know?

705
00:37:45,310 --> 00:37:46,390
Unlike a certain individual.

